  - Any form of automated content ingestion for AI product development

This prohibition applies regardless of whether the use is commercial or
non-commercial, and applies universally to all entities, including but not
limited to:

  OpenAI, Google (DeepMind), Anthropic, Meta AI, Mistral AI, Perplexity AI,
